Token.comment: Circle(X,Y,r[,{i) will draw a circle at (X,Y) with radius r. X and Y will be affected by the window settings. The radius will also be affected by the window settings. If a complex list such as {i} is passed to Circle( as the fourth argument, the 'fast circle' routine is used instead.
